<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Responsum</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrapper case-study responsum">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Responsum</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Helping patients&nbsp;<br />help themselves.</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Patient Support Platform</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We designed an online community where patients of rare conditions can get curated, medically-verified news and support from other patients, all in one place.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded blue">
      <div class="container row between">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            What You Don't Know&nbsp;<br />Could Kill You
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            For rare conditions, online searches invite dead ends, misinformation, and even potentially lethal remedies. And users are often searching on their own.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Curate and&nbsp;<br />Congregate
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            We built an online community around an algorithm that prioritizes medically-accurate articles, tailored to each patient, that can be shared with specialists, loved ones and more.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block gray">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section1-card1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section1-card2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section1-card3.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left padded">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Getting to know you</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              With rare conditions, every patient's journey is unique. We created a behavior loop where users get immediate value, while training the algorithm along the way.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block extra-padded off-white">
      <div class="container">
        <img src="./images/work/responsum/section2-levels.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-left"> 
        <img src="./images/work/responsum/section2-icon.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-right">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block column half-md hide-overflow">
        <div class="inner-box">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle4.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-circle5.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart4.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-chart5.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-top">
        </div>
        <div class="inner-box off-white">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-reveal">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-reveal">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-reveal">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction4.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-reveal">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-reaction5.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-reveal">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md violet">
        <div class="container">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-tooltip1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-left">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section3-tooltip2.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-right">
        </div>
      </div>      
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Head and heart</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Learning about clinical trials doesn't have to feel clinical. We balanced credible resources with warm, comforting design cues.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-bottom shadow sr-bottom">
            <img src="./images/work/responsum/desktop-3.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block column padded half-md hide-overflow pink">
        <div class="container">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section5-card1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-top">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section5-card2.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain absolute sr-bottom">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">A clear picture&nbsp;<br />of health</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            On the road to recovery, every detail matters. We created an intuitive workflow that makes it easy for patients to keep track of their treatments, procedures, and visits.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>      
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img src="./images/work/responsum/icons.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Helping patients take control</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Setting goals - and keeping them - is something any patient can do, to help take back control over their condition. Our UI balances inspirational objectives with customizable progress tracking.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-bottom shadow sr-bottom">
            <img src="./images/work/responsum/desktop-1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img src="./images/work/responsum/banner.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">From living room&nbsp;<br />to waiting room</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Learning about a condition shouldn't be left at home. Our responsive interfaces let patients bring the articles and issues that matter the most right to their doctor's ppointments, with easily verifiable sources.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column padded half-md hide-overflow teal responsum-mobile">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="frame frame-mobile light sr-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img src="./images/work/responsum/mobile-1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile light absolute-bottom sr-right">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/responsum/mobile-2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Care that shares</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            When your condition is one in a million, finding local support is challenging. By providing ways for patients to share, react or follow content, we lay the groundwork for a positive, inclusive and welcoming environment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row responsum-devices">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <img src="./images/work/responsum/section7-container.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop absolute edge-bottom shadow sr-bottom">
            <img src="./images/work/responsum/desktop-2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile absolute light sr-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img src="./images/work/responsum/mobile-3.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral centered row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column blue">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
